	<pre class="propdef">
	Name: tab-size
	Value: <<number>> | <<length>>
	Initial: 8
	Applies to: text
	Inherited: yes
	Computed value: the specified number or absolute length
	Animation type: by computed value type
	Canonical order: n/a
	</pre>

	<wpt>
